     "type": "html",
     "name": "question21",
     "tag": "Optimum Html",
     "html": "I acknowledge:\n\n<ul>\n<li>The statements and information I have provided on this application will be used to determine my eligibility for UI benefits and are subject to verification.</li>\n<li>I may be guilty of fraud if I make false statements, provide false information, or knowingly withhold information to receive benefits.</li>\n<li>If I commit UI fraud, I may be fined, penalized, and criminally prosecuted.</li>\n<li>The information I provide to Iowa Workforce Development (IWD) may be made available to federal, state or local agencies and their subcontractors who administer employment and training programs.</li>\n<li>I must repay any UI benefits paid to me that I am not eligible to receive.</li>\n<li>I must file a weekly claim to request a benefit payment.</li>\n<li>I must report any income earned while I am filing to collect UI benefits.</li>\n<li>I must report any issues that might affect my ability to work or availability for work.</li>\n<li>I must report any separation that happens while I am filing to collect UI benefits.</li>\n<li>I must report if I refuse a job offer or referral.</li>\n<li>I must report any issues that limit my availability to work or attend training.</li>\n<li>I am required to know my rights and responsibilities while claiming UI benefits.</li>\n<li>I am required to contact the UI customer service if I have questions about my responsibilities or requirements of receiving UI benefits.</li>\n</ul>\n<br><br>\t\nI certify:\n<ul>\n<li>I will read the Unemployment Insurance Handbook.</li>\n<li>I am totally or partially unemployed.</li>\n<li>I am able to work or attend training.</li>\n<li>I am registered for work by filing this application.</li>\n<li>Statements I have made on this application and all attachments to it are true, accurate, and complete to the best of my knowledge and belief.</li>\n</ul>"
    },
